            "id": "PRRC_kwDOS97bAM7QWlpw",
            "body": "Addressed in 6393497: `staged_updates.rs` no longer imports or returns `ApiError`. It now exposes a staged-update domain error, and the current Git/API callers translate that to `ApiError` at the adapter edge. Existing broader domain modules still use `ApiError`, but this PR no longer adds that coupling in the new staged update boundary.",
            "createdAt": "2026-06-30T01:14:35Z",
